Package org.apache.sis.geometry

Class UnmodifiableGeometryException

  • Object
    • Throwable
      • Exception
        • RuntimeException
          • UnsupportedOperationException
            • UnmodifiableGeometryException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class UnmodifiableGeometryException
extends UnsupportedOperationException
    Indicates that an operation is not allowed on a geometry object because it is unmodifiable. Note that unmodifiable geometries are not necessarily immutable; they are just not allowed to be modified through the set­Foo(...) method that raised this exception. Whatever an unmodifiable geometry is immutable or not is implementation dependent.
    Since:
    0.3
